Chatbot service

How to use chatbot.py

1. make .env , can copy from .env.example
2. install requirements.txt
3. run chatbot.py
4. first run [POST] http://127.0.0.1:5000/start_chat, to get session_id. 
        output return json
        {
            "session_id": ""
        }
5. how to use chatbot, [POST]http://127.0.0.1:5000/chat, with raw - json:
        {
            "session_id": "",
            "message": ""
        }

        output return json:
        {
            "reply": ""
        }

